Package dog.giraffe

Interface Log

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClusteringStrategy<P>, Image, ImageReader, ImageWriter, InitialCenters<P>, ReplaceEmptyCluster<P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BufferedImageReader, BufferedImageWriter, Cluster1, Cluster2, FileImageReader, FileImageWriter, Hue, HyperHue, Image.Abstract, Image.Transform, Intensity, Normalize, NormalizedDifferenceVegetationIndex, NormalizedHyperHue, Select
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.
    @FunctionalInterface
public interface Log
    Supertype of classes that can log metadata.
